description: DEED RESTRICTED UNIT!  Household (HH) size 1/Max income $114,300/ HH 2, $130,600/ HH 3, $146,900/HH 4, $163,200,  all with max HH assets $100k (excluding retirement)  Welcome to your urban oasis: city living in the heart of south Boston in the Allele Building-- just 1 min walking (233' away) per Google Maps from Broadway T Stop and walking distance to restaurant/retail lined W Broadway --come home to your spacious 2 bedroom condo with floor to ceiling windows and patio that faces enclosed common area grounds complete with trees and plants! Owner removed a former 3rd bedroom to enjoy an open plan living, which combined with the high ceilings gives an airy feel to the the unit!  Other room listed is a large utility room that owner uses as extra storage. In unit laundry!  FY25 taxes includes residential exemption.
